

#####SETUP A NODE APP#########################

mkdir /frontend
cd frontend
npm init
###Answer questions######
npm install express --save (Add express to our package.json as a dependency)

npm install (You only need this if you deploy your app in prod and the system needs to get all your dependencies)



#######Auto restart your server#########

##You can use nodemon or pm2
sudo npm install -g nodemon

###OR#####
sudo npm install -g pm2  ##I prefer pm2
